4: H-hmph! That was just a fluke!

trying to get someone else's

50:
...What do you mean I'm no

Luik...
71:

never checked into school. He's

83:

we're heading back.
88:
You don't care about me anyway! I

98:
Who said you could compare me to
anyone else, huh?!
102:
Anyone who's ever looked down on
me... Abandoned me... They never

106:
I'm not anyone else but myself! I got

112:

115:

118:

you sure you should be scolding him

cleaning up the mess first.

...I can't stop shaking. My legs won't

145:

154:
Also, I... What I said earlier... I know

164:

167:
We should head home too. I'm
starving.
171:
...If you have something to say, then
just say it.
174:

something?
178:
...I'll have you know that I despise
you.
181:

184:
If you have a problem with me, then
just say it.
188:

195:
...Yeah, I never liked that part of you
either.
